Southeast Beauty! - Wow! This One Is A Beauty! Super Willow Wood Neighborhood *Easy Living 1 Story, Bright Open Floor Plan, New Plush Carpet, Fresh Paint, Immaculate! Super Kit/ Bay Windowed Breakfast Nook, 2 Large Patios(One Covered),Lots Of Ceramic Tile, Great Closet Space, Great Rm.W/Charming Fireplace, Built-in Book Shelves & Cathedral Ceiling*Fabulous Mbr Suite W/Patio Access*Arched Doorways**Easy Commute To Kafb,Sandia Labs, Shopping*Its A Winner* Just Move& Enjoy When applying please consider some of our application guidelines below: Recommend 3x income of monthly rent. Recommend above 600 Credit Score. $50.00 app fee per adult (above 18). Provide 2 months of most recent bank statements. Most recent pay stub to verify employment, or recent tax return if self-employed. Copy of photo your I.D. If you have any pets please attach their photos and proof of rabies vaccination. Lease Term: 12 months All documents can be uploaded in multiple formats by applying online. Call TODAY to set up an appointment (505)796-1400
